Generator mounted SimpleChangelog in your config/routes.rb file:
	mount SimpleChangelog::Engine => "/simple_changelog", as: "simple_changelog"
It will also generate simple_changelog_url and simple_changelog_uri methods

SimpleChangelog::RepositoriesHelper has been connected to your app.
You can use the following methods:
	#long_date_format(datetime)
   	#highlight_commit_tags(commit_message)	
    #current_version_tag
    